.600" end="1:47.830">無</span><span begin="1:47.830" end="1:48.180">法</span><span begin="1:48.180" end="1:48.890">眷</span><span begin="1:48.890" end="1:49.500">戀</span><span begin="1:49.500" end="1:49.790">得</span><span begin="1:50.130" end="1:50.390">完</span><span begin="1:50.390" end="1:53.270">全</span></text><text for="L22"><span begin="2:11.040" end="2:11.230">或</span><span begin="2:11.230" end="2:11.650">許</span><span begin="2:11.650" end="2:11.900">該</span><span begin="2:11.900" end="2:12.270">學</span><span begin="2:12.270" end="2:12.500">著</span><span begin="2:12.500" end="2:12.870">石</span><span begin="2:12.870" end="2:13.260">頭</span><span begin="2:13.260" end="2:13.480">忘</span><span begin="2:13.480" end="2:13.740">卻</span><span begin="2:13.740" end="2:14.120">世</span><span begin="2:14.120" end="2:14.430">界</span><span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="2:10.760" end="2:13.050">(ha~</span> <span begin="2:13.250" end="2:13.480">忘</span><span begin="2:13.480" end="2:13.740">卻</span><span begin="2:13.740" end="2:14.130">世</span><span begin="2:14.130" end="2:14.570">界)</span></span></text><text for="L23"><span begin="2:14.820" end="2:15.090">也</span><span begin="2:15.090" end="2:15.440">貪</span><span begin="2:15.440" end="2:15.730">婪</span><span begin="2:15.730" end="2:16.060">一</span><span begin="2:16.060" end="2:16.840">點</span> <span begin="2:17.310" end="2:17.600">也</span><span begin="2:17.600" end="2:17.840">單</span><span begin="2:17.840" end="2:18.220">純</span><span begin="2:18.220" end="2:19.180">一</span><span begin="2:19.180" end="2:20.190">點</span></text><text for="L24"><span begin="2:21.070" end="2:21.370">等</span><span begin="2:21.370" end="2:21.660">到</span><span begin="2:21.660" end="2:22.010">又</span><span begin="2:22.010" end="2:22.240">一</span><span begin="2:22.240" end="2:22.570">顆</span><span begin="2:22.570" end="2:22.890">月</span><span begin="2:22.890" end="2:23.180">也</span><span begin="2:23.180" end="2:23.560">沉</span><span begin="2:23.560" end=